{"tid":47746,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔神英雄傳》導演井內秀治離世 享年66歲","createTime":"2016-12-20T14:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T13:07:10.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29c0f999c30d0bfa85706f493b21b4de0bc63a0d","tid":47746,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"日本動畫界最近傳來令人惋惜之消息，曾製作多齣經典動畫的66歲資深動畫家井內秀治，昨晚傳來離世噩耗，他曾為大家熟悉的《魔神英雄傳》、《魔動王》、《媽媽是小學四年生》等擔任導演及劇本等工作，套套都是動畫迷的童年回憶，其死訊令亞洲各地觀眾及網友都感到可惜。<br />\n<br />\n井內秀治於70年代加入動畫界，入行初期參與過《宇宙戰艦大和號》、《銀河鐵道999》等，近年則有《Keroro軍曹》，不過論到屬於井內秀治的代表作就要首推《魔神英雄傳》、《魔動王》，由他負責監督工作，動畫大師蘆田豐雄擔任人物設定，二人可謂最佳拍檔，之後92年的《媽媽是小學四年生》同樣大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n不少動畫界人士及網民，近日於網上留言悼念井內秀治，據知井內秀治是在上周四離世，暫時未有公佈其死因。"},{"pid":"2af5559ace84d875ba2fec0ed0f8eca173b01636","tid":47746,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fc2b206ff5eba6010161884bf8a1fe33673e8a","tid":47746,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"機會黎啦飛雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2db46adaedb404d9ae5767898ce7a0287b64bf7","tid":47746,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"魔動王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b93f00473375b1034a1ed1e5692e2b09c1f4633","tid":47746,"uid":45430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"人生仲會有幾多個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a7d7845b7d466dbb7c55565e2a93eefe8faaa6","tid":47746,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgm